, 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/8673/', '', 'Clevidipine, Mibefradil, Celecoxib, Propranolol, Metoprolol, Carvedilol, Nebivolol, Bisoprolol, Ivabradine, Sotalol, Acetylsalicylic acid, Atenolol', 'Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Diroximel fumarate, Abatacept, Apremilast, Inebilizumab, Belumosudil, Belimumab, Sutimlimab, Risankizumab, More', 1767369485);
